Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: Shining the light on payola
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b03zjn63
Last Broadcast Date: Sun 21 Nov 1976
Carter promises more than the Sunshine laws to shed light on payola. This archive edition of Letter from America was recorded by one of two listeners, who between them taped and labelled over 650 Letter From America programmes from 1973 to 1989. It was restored by the BBC in 2014.